<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="speech-n">speech <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /spiːtʃ/    美 /spiːtʃ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>演说；发言：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>deliver / give / make a speech</strong>
发表演说</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>an opening / a closing speech
开/闭幕词</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>说话；言语：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>freedom of speech</strong>
言论自由</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Speech is the mirror of action.
语言是行动的镜子。</p></div></div>